-------------------------------------------------------------------
P1 VS COMP
==========

KEYS: (KEYS must be selected as PLAYER 1 controls)
==================================================
A     -  Accelerate
Z     -  Brake
<     -  Turn Left
>     -  Turn Right
TAB   -  Cycle through features (Turbo, Oil, SuperGrip)
SPACE -  Activate selected feature
ALT   -  Reverse
--------------------------------------------------------------------

P1 VS P2 (Not available in demo)
========

PLAYER 1 KEYS: (KEYS must be selected as PLAYER 1 controls)
===========================================================
Q     -  Accelerate
A     -  Brake
S     -  Turn Left
D     -  Turn Right
TAB   -  Cycle through features (Turbo, Oil, SuperGrip)
ALT   -  Activate selected feature
Z     -  Reverse

PLAYER 2 KEYS: (KEYS must be selected as PLAYER 2 controls)
===========================================================
L               -  Accelerate
.               -  Brake
LEFT ARROW      -  Turn Left
RIGHT ARROW     -  Turn Right
I               -  Cycle through features (Turbo, Oil, SuperGrip)
CTRL            -  Activate selected feature
DOWN ARROW      -  Reverse

---------------------------------------------------------------------

JOY 1: (JOY 1 must be selected as PLAYER 1 controls)
====================================================
Push forward    -  Accelerate
Pull back       -  Brake (Reverse if stationary)
Push left       -  Turn left
Push right      -  Turn right
Button 1        -  Select feature
Button 2        -  Activate feature

JOY 2: (JOY 2 must be selected as PLAYER 2 controls)
====================================================
Push forward    -  Accelerate
Pull back       -  Brake (Reverse if stationary)
Push left       -  Turn left
Push right      -  Turn right
Button 1        -  Select feature
Button 2        -  Activate feature

-----------------------------------------------------------------

CUSTOM 1: (CUSTOM 1 must be selected as PLAYER 1 controls)
==========================================================

Joy1 Button 1     -  Accelerate
Joy1 Button 2     -  Brake
Joy1 Push left    -  Turn left
Joy1 Push right   -  Turn right
TAB               -  Cycle through features (Turbo, Oil, SuperGrip)
ALT               -  Activate selected feature
Z                 -  Reverse

CUSTOM 2: (CUSTOM 2 must be selected as PLAYER 2 controls)
==========================================================

Joy2 Button 1     -  Accelerate
Joy2 Button 2     -  Brake
Joy2 Push left    -  Turn left
Joy2 Push right   -  Turn right
I                 -  Cycle through features (Turbo, Oil, SuperGrip)
CTRL              -  Activate selected feature
Z                 -  Reverse

-------------------------------------------------------------------

THRUSTMASTER T1: (THRUSTMASTER T1 must be selected as PLAYER 1 controls)
========================================================================

Right Pedal       -  Accelerate
Left Pedal        -  Brake
Turn wheel left   -  Turn left
Turn wheel right  -  Turn right
Pull stick back   -  Cycle through features (Turbo, Oil, SuperGrip)
Push stick forward-  Activate selected feature
Button A          -  Reverse

-------------------------------------------------------------------

Other controls:
===============
PgUp  -  Hi Res (default)
PgDn  -  Low Res
End   -  Toggle sky on/off
-     -  Shrink screen
+     -  Grow screen
Esc   -  Exit race
F     -  Show frame rate

Camera controls:

F1/F2 -  Select car to view

F3/F4 -  Select camera in the following order
                ChaseCam (default)
                LeftCam
                RevserveCam
                RightCam
                HeadCam
                LeftVRCam
                ForwardVRCam
                RightVRCam
                ZoomCam1
                ZoomCam2
                ZoomCam3

F5/F6 -  Rotate camera (Not available on ZoomCam)

F7/F8 -  Zoom in/out (Not available on ZoomCam)

F9/F10-  Adjust 'padlock' view. This follows the direction that your
         head would be pointing as you go round a corner to give the
         impression of 'G' force.

Short cuts to camera:

ALT-F1     -  Select ZoomCam1
ALT-F2     -  Select ZoomCam2
ALT-F3     -  Select ZoomCam3
ALT-F4     -  Select ChaseCam
ALT-F5     -  Select LeftCam
ALT-F6     -  Select RevserveCam
ALT-F7     -  Select RightCam
ALT-F8     -  Select HeadCam
ALT-F9     -  Select LeftVRCam
ALT-F10    -  Select ForwardVRCam
ALT-F11    -  Select RightVRCam





